If activated your camera centers if any key is pressed.

consoleCommands.resetUIAndZoom.descripti:
Usage: reset_UI_and_Zoom <ui> <zoom>
- ui: the decimal value UI scale.
- zoom: the decimal value zoom level.
consoleCommands.resetUI.name: reset_UI
consoleCommands.resetUI.description:

- ui: the decimal value UI scale.
consoleCommands.resetZoom.name: reset_Zoom
consoleCommands.reset_Zoom.description:
Usage: reset_Zoom <zoom>
- zoom: the decimal value zoom level.
consoleMessages.listingOfCommands.messag:
zoom_Level_List → Shows all the ZoomLevel console commands.

toggle_Auto_Zoom_Map → Toggles the 'AutoZoomMap'.

toggle_Press_Any_Key_To_Reset_Camera → Toggles the 'PressAnyKeyToResetCamera'.

toggle_Hide_With_UI_With_Certain_Zoom → Toggles the 'HideWithUIWithCertainZoom'.

reset_UI_and_Zoom → Resets the zoom and UI levels back to the default game values.
Optional parameters UI and Zoom values (in that order).

reset_UI → Resets the UI scale.
Optional parameter is the UI Scale value.

reset_Zoom → Resets the Zoom Level.
Optional parameter is the Zoom Level value.
